The paper deals with estimation of linear dynamical systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of networked observations and communication constraints suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.MA), information theory (cs.IT), networked systems (cs.NI), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
